dc_title_s: Spring Aerial Imagery Photo Center Points and Acquisition Dates, 2009-2014: Minnesota
dc_description_s: This dataset contains the center point locations for all images acquired under the Minnesota Spring Aerial Imagery Program from 2009 through 2014. Attributes for each center point include the photo file ID, the center point location, the date of acquisition, and the vendor. Additional attributes for acquisition altitude and camera system are also provided where available.
dc_creator_sm: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources and Minnesota Geospatial Information Office
